    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The Last Nightmare</i> is a top-down game with a pixelated style, combining pixel art with 3D models. Experience the journey of the protagonist as he tries to return home, facing various challenges and unimaginable creatures. Utilize the mechanics of</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Lantern</u></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/dbad086a22ce0b75cd9089a1f8d8aa1e.poster.avif?t=1765236233\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/dbad086a22ce0b75cd9089a1f8d8aa1e.webm?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/dbad086a22ce0b75cd9089a1f8d8aa1e.mp4?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Use it to explore the depths of darkness and uncover the mysteries it hides.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Items and Inventory</u></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/7208d38f0d6bf57c71b7080ed4687ed7.poster.avif?t=1765236233\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/7208d38f0d6bf57c71b7080ed4687ed7.webm?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/7208d38f0d6bf57c71b7080ed4687ed7.mp4?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Collect all the items you find; while some will be useful immediately, others will serve as keys to open doors and chests. Additionally, there are cards that reveal hidden parts of the story, encouraging you to investigate every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Running and Stamina System</u></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/44288dfcee02b116efba12e8cf90ee2f.poster.avif?t=1765236233\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/44288dfcee02b116efba12e8cf90ee2f.webm?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/44288dfcee02b116efba12e8cf90ee2f.mp4?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Extremely useful for escaping from monsters, but be careful not to exhaust yourself. Balance is crucial for ensuring your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Stealth</u></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/14e2454054804c58dc1d9c2dfb8e0d8a.poster.avif?t=1765236233\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/14e2454054804c58dc1d9c2dfb8e0d8a.webm?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/14e2454054804c58dc1d9c2dfb8e0d8a.mp4?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel the sound of your breath and heartbeat. This mode is very useful for hiding from certain monsters, but remember: you are not invisible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Explore the world and the story around you.</u></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/3ac3c6ab6b164d2e823e241b045000f3.poster.avif?t=1765236233\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/3ac3c6ab6b164d2e823e241b045000f3.webm?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/3ac3c6ab6b164d2e823e241b045000f3.mp4?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/e15cca6b26107b5fb897537cee56744a.poster.avif?t=1765236233\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/e15cca6b26107b5fb897537cee56744a.webm?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231370/extras/e15cca6b26107b5fb897537cee56744a.mp4?t=1765236233\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
